-Do you agree with me?
-Yes.

333
00:19:58,488 --> 00:19:59,323
Then...

334
00:19:59,406 --> 00:20:02,951
Around your house

335
00:20:03,035 --> 00:20:07,080
I fiddle with my phone

336
00:20:07,164 --> 00:20:08,957
-I muster up my courage
-What is it now?

337
00:20:09,041 --> 00:20:10,626
-To call you
-You agreed. Why are you singing?

338
00:20:10,709 --> 00:20:12,211
I wasn't complaining.

339
00:20:13,545 --> 00:20:15,714
I don't know. It's become a habit.

340
00:20:15,797 --> 00:20:18,926
When I walk around

