355
00:20:56,380 --> 00:20:58,799
No. I gave it a lot of thought.

356
00:20:59,299 --> 00:21:01,510
I can't always learn from the superiors.

357
00:21:01,593 --> 00:21:04,263
The younger ones lead the trend.

358
00:21:04,346 --> 00:21:07,557
