368
00:21:34,793 --> 00:21:38,380
So those two are working on a drama?

369
00:21:38,964 --> 00:21:39,965
Yes.

370
00:21:46,680 --> 00:21:47,931
Are you upset?

371
00:21:48,473 --> 00:21:51,393
I told you to simply ignore him.
That's the easy way.

372
00:21:51,810 --> 00:21:54,980
No. He's making me think about
a lot of things.

373
00:21:55,522 --> 00:21:57,024
No matter what they do
to change the trend,

374
00:21:57,107 --> 00:21:58,650
