387
00:22:28,096 --> 00:22:30,223
And I know you're about to call my name.

388
00:22:30,307 --> 00:22:33,769
Don't call me.
I said, do not call my name.

389
00:22:34,478 --> 00:22:37,189
Hye-jeong. Ms. Jung, come on.

390
00:22:37,522 --> 00:22:39,024
