406
00:23:14,101 --> 00:23:16,686
you see his tears are beige colored
because of the foundation.

407
00:23:16,770 --> 00:23:18,438
Did you hear me? Beige tears.

408
00:23:18,647 --> 00:23:20,565
You're right. It's a disaster.

409
00:23:20,816 --> 00:23:21,650
Now,

410
00:23:21,817 --> 00:23:24,820
you're telling me to put this
on my face then take it off.

411
00:23:25,445 --> 00:23:26,696
What do you think will happen?

412
00:23:28,031 --> 00:23:30,784
My whole face will be covered
in beige tears.

