505
00:30:01,341 --> 00:30:03,885
Eun-jeong, you're curious, aren't you?

506
00:30:04,928 --> 00:30:05,762
What do you mean?

507
00:30:05,845 --> 00:30:07,722
You said you wanted to work on people

508
00:30:07,806 --> 00:30:09,766
instead of social issues this time.

509
00:30:09,849 --> 00:30:13,061
Yes, I did. So what?

510
00:30:15,438 --> 00:30:18,024
-Lee So-min?
-Yes. I like the idea.

